{"parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "The Platform"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "Guides"}], "prev": {"link": "../../", "title": "Guides"}, "next": {"link": "../criteria_options/", "title": "Criteria Options"}, "title": "Commenting", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"commenting\">\n<h1>Commenting<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#commenting\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\">You should navigate to the page on which you want to comment using the <i class=\"fa fa-bars\"></i> in the ribbon.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">Comments can be viewed by anyone who has access to the feature you are commenting under.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Click the bar entitled <strong>Write a comment\u2026</strong> and type your comment</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p>Add an emoji by clicking the <i class=\"fa fa-smile\"></i> and selecting an emoji</p></li>\n<li><p>Add an image by clicking the <i class=\"fa fa-camera\"></i> and selecting an image</p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>If desired, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/how_to_upload_a_file.html\">upload</a> a file</p></li>\n<li><p>Hit enter or return</p></li>\n<li><p>To reply to a comment, hover over the comment and click the <i class=\"fa fa-circle-left\"></i></p></li>\n<li><p>To react to a comment, hover over the comment, click the <i class=\"fa fa-smile\"></i> and choose emoji</p></li>\n<li><p>To delete a comment, hover over the comment and click the <i class=\"fa fa-times\"></i></p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/criteria_options", "Criteria Options", "N", "next"], ["users/general/guides/index", "Guides", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/comment.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Commenting</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/comment", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}